                <div class="help-text" style="margin-top: 10px;">
                  <strong>Available tags:</strong><br>
                  <code style="background: #f1f5f9; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;">{{CustomerName}}</code> - Customer's first name (or "there" if unknown)<br>
                  <code style="background: #f1f5f9; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;">{{BusinessName}}</code> - Your business name<br>
                  <code style="background: #f1f5f9; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px;">{{ReviewLink}}</code> - Your review platform link <span style="color: #dc2626;">(required)</span>
